<h2 id="content">Content</h2>
<p>To implement the project, the author built a specialized hardware-software complex for recording and processing frame-by-frame animation. The main material used in the animation is metal nails of various sizes.<br />
Class ‚ÄúTrick der Sterne‚Äù by prof. Kati Barath, Ulike Isenberg (WiSe20-21)</p>

<h2 id="presentation">Presentation</h2>
<p>The work was screened at the TrickFilm Abendfestival, Galerie des Westens, Bremen, Germany, 09.10.2021</p>

